hu.elte.txtuml.api.assocends.Multiplicity

  • Packages that use Multiplicity 
    Package Description
    hu.elte.txtuml.api
    Provides the txtUML modeling API.
    hu.elte.txtuml.api.assocends
    Contains some interfaces which provide an abstraction to association end properties, like navigability and multiplicity.
